div.div: Official 4-koma manga adaptation based on the anime series written by mato and serialized in Shounen Jump+. It features chibi versions of the characters and retells the story in a caricaturing way. Note: For every episode of DARLING in the FRANXX, there are 3 chapters/pages illustrating the events of the episode, with the exception of the final episode, which had 4 chapters.
Mushoku Tensei: Roxy datte Honki desu

A series about the life of popular character Roxy from the popular series Mushoku Tensei. Having discovered that she has been born without her race's racial ability, Roxy went through a childhood of isolation, but her chance meeting with a magician broadened her horizons. What awaited the young girl that, looking for freedom, left her hometown was...! Contains spoilers for Mushoku Tensei: Isekai Ittara Honki Dasu.
